- `std::vector & Container Internals` — How RAII makes containers safe
- `Move Semantics & Perfect Forwarding` — Rule of Five's move operations
- https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/raii
- https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/rule_of_three

