- [[04 — OOP & Generics/03 — C++ Casting & RTTI|Casting & RTTI]] — Pure C++ casting
- [[03 — Memory/03 — Smart Pointers & Ownership|Smart Pointers]] — Pure C++ smart pointers
- [[02 — Syntax & Types/09 — String Types & string_view|String Types]] — Pure C++ strings
- [[04 — OOP & Generics/05 — Templates & Concepts|Templates]] — How `if constexpr` and SFINAE work
- Pointer Ecosystem (UE) — `TObjectPtr`, `TSharedPtr`, `TUniquePtr`
- Casting in Unreal Engine — `Cast<T>()`, `IsA<T>()`, `ExactCast<T>()`

